## 4. Complete Protocol Message Reference

### Public Update Messages (handle all of these)

**Battle Setup:** `|player|`, `|teamsize|`, `|gametype|`, `|gen|`, `|tier|`, `|rule|`, `|start`, `|clearpoke`, `|poke|`, `|teampreview`, `|t:|`

**Turn Flow:** `|turn|N`, `|upkeep`

**Actions:** `|move|POKEMON|MOVE|TARGET`, `|switch|POKEMON|DETAILS|HP STATUS`, `|drag|POKEMON|DETAILS|HP STATUS`, `|replace|POKEMON|DETAILS`

**Damage/Healing (via split):** `|-damage|POKEMON|HP STATUS`, `|-heal|POKEMON|HP STATUS`, `|-sethp|POKEMON|HP STATUS`

**Status:** `|-status|POKEMON|STATUS`, `|-curestatus|POKEMON|STATUS`, `|-cureteam|POKEMON`

**Stat Changes:** `|-boost|POKEMON|STAT|AMOUNT`, `|-unboost|POKEMON|STAT|AMOUNT`, `|-setboost|POKEMON|STAT|AMOUNT`, `|-clearboost|POKEMON`, `|-clearallboost`, `|-clearpositiveboost|POKEMON`, `|-clearnegativeboost|POKEMON`, `|-swapboost|SOURCE|TARGET|STATS`

**Abilities/Items:** `|-ability|POKEMON|ABILITY`, `|-endability|POKEMON`, `|-item|POKEMON|ITEM`, `|-enditem|POKEMON|ITEM`

**Field Effects:** `|-weather|WEATHER`, `|-fieldstart|CONDITION`, `|-fieldend|CONDITION`, `|-fieldactivate|EFFECT`, `|-sidestart|SIDE|CONDITION`, `|-sideend|SIDE|CONDITION`

**Combat Results:** `|-supereffective|POKEMON`, `|-resisted|POKEMON`, `|-crit|POKEMON`, `|-miss|SOURCE|TARGET`, `|-immune|POKEMON`, `|-fail|POKEMON`, `|faint|POKEMON`, `|-hitcount|POKEMON|COUNT`, `|-killed|POKEMON` (custom)

**Forme/Transform:** `|detailschange|POKEMON|DETAILS`, `|-formechange|POKEMON|SPECIES`, `|-transform|POKEMON|TARGET`, `|-mega|POKEMON|STONE`, `|-primal|POKEMON`

**Volatile Status:** `|-start|POKEMON|EFFECT`, `|-end|POKEMON|EFFECT`, `|-activate|POKEMON|EFFECT`, `|-singleturn|POKEMON|MOVE`

**Other:** `|cant|POKEMON|REASON`, `|-mustrecharge|POKEMON`, `|-prepare|POKEMON|MOVE`, `|-nothing`, `|-anim|SOURCE|MOVE|TARGET`

**End:** `|win|PLAYER`, `|tie`

